{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-notes-template-tsx","path":"/process-manager","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>A process manager is used to continually run the app. He uses PM2.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token comment\"># Install PM2</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\"># sudo is used because this is installed globally</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> <span class=\"token function\">npm</span> i -g pm2\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># Start PM2</span>\npm2 start app.js\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># Setup auto restart</span>\npm2 startup</code></pre></div>","frontmatter":{"path":"/process-manager","title":"Process Manager","order":"l"}}},"pageContext":{}}}